  "texts": [
    "According to the World Economic Forum, such health misinformation contributed to increased vaccine hesitancy in multiple countries.",
    "The public, already fearful due to the pandemic, encountered what looked like factual reports, not realizing they were computational concoctions.",
    "This demonstrates how AI-generated text can amplify the reach of harmful falsehoods by sheer quantity and the illusion of legitimacy, thereby undermining public trust in health authorities and complicating crisis responses.",
    "In the political realm, AI text generators have been harnessed to produce persuasive messaging at a volume and personalization level not achievable before.",
